{"type": "article", "id": 28972, "title": "竹凳", "description": "", "date": "2016-07-01T06:49:09Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 42, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160703123335X0bmSe7s3TPOGVwc.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>竹子在不少东南亚的国家和地区被视为一种常见且环保的材料，并且在各地发展出了独特的竹艺文化，比如我们不久前曾经介绍过的<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/28408.html\">竹制音响</a>就采用了越南特有的工艺。来自台湾的 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/EvanHS\">Yi-Fan Hsieh</a> 就利用当地的毛竹（Moso）设计了名为“清转合”的竹凳系列：一米长的毛竹被分隔成三片后进行了切割和热弯处理，最后利用胶合剂和钉子组合在一起。为了加强稳固性，Hsieh 还推出了四方形的竹凳，简洁明了的结构与竹子青翠坚韧的特性相结合，看起来既清爽又优雅，是一个很适合夏天的设计。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703123333nCUa39J2RzbmdFSw.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.96830986\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607031233336pdhkEcqLT8Igx25.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.73888889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607031233348PfCBawznNREKQer.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703123334agUAdMykXZR87o0q.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.95185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}